166
00:09:01,065 --> 00:09:03,807
Pourquoi tu crois
que je cherchais un partenaire ?

167
00:09:04,511 --> 00:09:07,487
- Je sais pas, Cliff.
- Allez, on le fera ensemble.

168
00:09:07,789 --> 00:09:10,472
Deux mecs qui se rasent, bronzent,

169
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:12,135
